properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 8 at 3:08AM PST until February 10 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Owens Valley.

* WHEN...From 10 AM Sunday to 10 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Blowind dust may reduce visibility in spots near the Owens Lake.
Strong crosswinds on east-west oriented roads can make driving
difficult...especially for motorcycles and high profile
vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle on east-west oriented roads. Secure outdoor
objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM SUNDAY TO 10 AM PST MONDAY
